Package: TaxaID
Type: Package
Title: Probabilistic Taxonomic Assignment for eDNA, Acoustic, and Image Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Kevin", "Lafferty", email = "klafferty@usgs.gov",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Meta-package that installs the full TaxaID ecosystem.
    Provides probabilistic taxonomic assignment via likelihood, prior, and
    posterior probability for eDNA metabarcoding, acoustic detection, and
    image classification data.
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
